definition: Belgium/Belgian/abbr. for 比利時|比利时[Bi3 li4 shi2]
to compare/(followed by a noun and adjective) more {adj.} than {noun}/ratio/to gesture/(Taiwan pr. [bi4] in some compounds derived from Classical Chinese)
on top/upon/above/upper/previous/first (of multiple parts)/to climb/to get onto/to go up/to attend (class or university)

sentences.english: A lake of gold in the desert sand is less than a cool, fresh spring.
sentences.chinese: 沙漠中一湖的黄金也比不上一股清泉。

sentences.english: The packings and advertising propaganda of our company can't obviously compare with our competitor.
sentences.chinese: 我们公司在产品的包装和宣传上明显比不上竞争对手。

sentences.english: Although this method does not compare the perfect sexual affection, it is not also far.
sentences.chinese: 虽然这种方法式比不上完美的性爱，但是也相差不远。

sentences.english: Not as much as you did. Where do you put all that food?
sentences.chinese: 才比不上你呢。你怎么吃得下这么多？

sentences.english: There's nothing like seeing the whole action flowing back and forth.
sentences.chinese: 这远比不上亲眼看到整个来回的流畅动作。

sentences.english: Your fairness in business dealings is really unsurpassed.
sentences.chinese: 办理业务这么公平，真的谁也比不上你。

sentences.english: Its interchanges are so great that even Moscow is envious.
sentences.chinese: 它的交叉道巨大无比，甚至连莫斯科都比不上。

sentences.english: She has a very good notion of fingering, though her taste is not equal to Anne's.
sentences.chinese: 虽说她的趣味比不上安妮，可是她很懂得指法。

sentences.english: Polyester, for example, is less desirable than smooth knit.
sentences.chinese: 比如，涤纶就比不上平滑的针织材料。

sentences.english: Fairly, although it's not a box at the Royal Albert Hall, either.
sentences.chinese: 还可以，虽然比不上阿尔伯塔皇家剧院的包厢。

sentences.english: Lin Ying is not as good at sports as her sister.
sentences.chinese: 林英在体育方面比不上她的姐妹。

sentences.english: Your fairness in settling this claim is really unsurpassed.
sentences.chinese: 您处理这桩索赔案如此公平，真是谁也比不上。

sentences.english: There's no business like Internet business.
sentences.chinese: 什么行业也比不上网络业。

sentences.english: Greg : Money and games, but nothing beats this jacket Lindy gave me.
sentences.chinese: 但什么也比不上林迪送我的这件夹克。

sentences.english: Dynamo is not spatch on Liverpool.
Food they eat all day is not even equal your left over.
sentences.chinese: 牠们整天的进食量，恐怕还比不上您吃剩的。
